summary:
Hi, y’all!
I decided to start this blog because I love Haunter + I’m tired of them getting @‘d so much by others who think...
body:
Hi, y’all!

I decided to start this blog because I love Haunter + I’m tired of them getting @‘d so much by others who think Haunter has 0 potential / isn’t as cool as their evolved form, Gengar. Which is wrong, because, Haunter is one of the best Pokémon out there. 😔💜 I use mine all the time on my team, and she’s just the greatest.

Anyways: here’s a quick meme I made with an old template. :) please credit when reposted.

summary:
Inavember Pokezuma Day 3 - Aphrodi & Milotic 
I still can't believe Milotic was not my first thought for Aphrodi. It was Arceus...
body:
Inavember Pokezuma Day 3 - Aphrodi & Milotic

I still can’t believe Milotic was not my first thought for Aphrodi. It was Arceus and dear god i really didn’t wanted to draw them. My second thought was Luvdisc lmao. He probably does have one tho. But Milotic was the most obvious choice for this heavenly beautiful boy. So here we are !

Milotic is hella hard to draw

He named her Venus ~
